item.title: Kalina
item.description: ߷ This article is about an overseas member of the Commonwealth of Vekllei 1. Overview Although Vekllei comprises several independent commonwealths, most notably the island city-state to which it owes its name, the Commonwealth of Vekllei also includes several autonomous nations. The largest of these is a tropical archipelago of the Lesser Antilles named Kalina. K alina (commonly The Kalina Islands) is an autonomous commonwealth island chain situated in the Antilles, situated south-east of the British Virgin Islands and north of Guadeloupe.

item.title: West Antilles
item.description: ߷ This article is about an overseas member of the Commonwealth of Vekllei 1. Overview Making up the far reaches of Vekllei’s broad autonomous islander community, the West Antilles are full and autonomous members of the Atlantic Commonwealth. KT he West Antilles (commonly The Leeward Isles) is the common name of three autonomous islands that make up the West Antilles, situated offshore of northern Venezuala in the Caribbean Sea.
